83. Develop a PHP script to accept email addresses and validate it. Display the domain name of the
email and result of validation.

&lt;?php
$email = &quot;user@example.com&quot;;
if(filter_var($email, FILTER_VALIDATE_EMAIL)) {
$domain = substr(strrchr($email, &quot;@&quot;), 1);
echo &quot;Valid email. Domain: &quot; . $domain;
} else {
echo &quot;Invalid email.&quot;;
}
?&gt;
output:
Valid email. Domain: example.com
